title: Live Large!
posting_body: ['This luxury property has features and a full menu of amenities that will astound and complement an active lifestyle.', 'Floor plans are chic, sleek, filled with natural light and thoughtful details.', 'Be close to the urban diversity of CityLine, within walking distance to the Dart Arapaho Center Station, and convenient to major employers including State Farm and Cisco.', 'Live big here.', 'Call or text Spirit Real Estate Group ~', 'show contact info', '~ refer to R-GV-1.', 'If emailing about this ad, please include your full name, email address, best contact phone number, ideal move in date, and maximum rent amount.', 'This information will give us the best chance to match you with the apartment of your dreams!', 'We are one of the premier locating services in Dallas.', 'Our service is free', 'PLUS we will pay you a cash rebate or assist with your moving expenses (some restrictions may apply).', '<URL>', 'Facebook: Dallas Upscale Apartment Locators', 'Not all units have the same features or amenities pictured.', ' Availability, pricing, and specials are subject to change daily depending on market conditions.', 'Pricing or specials in the ads are not always updated accordingly.', '*Richardson*', 'We service Downtown Dallas, Uptown Dallas, Richardson, Highland Village, Old East Dallas, East Dallas, Frisco, Plano, North Dallas, Carrollton, Farmers Branch, Lewisville, Grapevine, Las Colinas, and all of the DFW Metroplex.', '**Ask us how to receive a cash rebate**']
